Class RMADetailsFormModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • RMA.RMAFormModel
      • RMA.RMADetailsFormModel
  • public class RMADetailsFormModel
extends RMAFormModel
    RMADetailsFormModel contains extended fields from RMAFormModel that display in RMADetailScreen.

      rmaProgress contains the Double value of the progress bar.
